The parameter estimates of the two main relationships of interest in the daily SEMs of the two cities are shown in Fig. 4, along with the standard error of these estimates. The coefficients \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
